cmu-medical-pain-mild-alert-name     = Aching
cmu-medical-pain-mild-alert-desc     = You feel mild pain. Movement and aim are slightly impaired.
cmu-medical-pain-moderate-alert-name = Hurt
cmu-medical-pain-moderate-alert-desc = You feel moderate pain. Movement and aim are impaired.
cmu-medical-pain-severe-alert-name   = Agony
cmu-medical-pain-severe-alert-desc   = You are in severe pain. Movement and aim are heavily impaired.
cmu-medical-pain-shock-pulse         = Pain shock overwhelms you!

cmu-medical-pain-reflection-mild-1 = Something aches.
cmu-medical-pain-reflection-mild-2 = You can still ignore the pain.
cmu-medical-pain-reflection-mild-3 = Your body keeps reminding you.

cmu-medical-pain-reflection-moderate-1 = This hurts. You need painkillers.
cmu-medical-pain-reflection-moderate-2 = Focus. Breathe. It still hurts.
cmu-medical-pain-reflection-moderate-3 = The pain keeps pulling at your thoughts.

cmu-medical-pain-reflection-severe-1 = Every movement hurts. Stop. No, move.
cmu-medical-pain-reflection-severe-2 = Painkillers. Need painkillers. Right now.
cmu-medical-pain-reflection-severe-3 = It is getting hard to think in full thoughts.

cmu-medical-pain-reflection-shock-1 = Too much. Too much. Make it stop.
cmu-medical-pain-reflection-shock-2 = Pain. Help. Now. Now.
cmu-medical-pain-reflection-shock-3 = Can't think. Can't breathe. Make it stop.

cmu-medical-pain-relief-1 = The painkiller starts to take the edge off.
cmu-medical-pain-relief-2 = The pain dulls. You can breathe a little easier.
cmu-medical-pain-relief-3 = The worst of it softens, for now.

cmu-medical-shrapnel-none = No embedded shrapnel is found.
cmu-medical-shrapnel-extract-verb = Remove shrapnel
cmu-medical-shrapnel-extract-start = You begin removing embedded shrapnel.
cmu-medical-shrapnel-extract-finish = Removed { $count } embedded fragment{ $count ->
    [one] {""}
   *[other] s
}.
cmu-medical-shrapnel-movement-pain = Embedded shrapnel shifts painfully.
